data.description:
Stunning 3,260 sq ft CUSTOM HOME on huge .67 acre lot, on a cul-de-sac in Prestigious Light House Pointe!ROOF REPLACED PRIOR TO CLOSING W/ FULL PRICE OFFER.Cypress wood beams accent the ceilings of the Great Room featuring barn doors, built in cabinetry, shelving, & fireplace! This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is built for Entertaining! Gourmet kitchen boasts Quartz counters, under cabinet lighting, real Brick Backsplash, Farmhouse Sink w/Industrial Faucet, & built in Pot-filler. $6k Stainless Steel 'Thor Kitchen' Range, featuring Double Oven, Convection, & 6 burner gas stove w/15,000 BTU Griddle!  Center island w/seating for four overlooks formal dining room w/tongue & groove cypress ceiling, accent lighting, contemporary crystal chandelier & brick accent wall! Master Suite features tray ceiling, barn door, two large closets w/built in wooden organizers, bidet, & one-of-a-kind wooden vanities w/raised porcelain sinks. Opulent Dual Shower complete w/smooth pebble flooring, rain-heads, & body sprayers. Additional bedrooms are oversized, flexible 4th bedroom could easily double as the Executive Office.

Massive 32x16 Bonus Room includes half bath & double French doors to the screened porch w/built in Wet Bar! Outdoor spaces continue to impress with lush greenery & Commanding Pergola. 10x12 Pergola Columns, buried 6ft into the ground with concrete, surround seating with swings, and steps to raised Spa.  (Conveys as-is) New AC in 2021, Water Heater in 2020. Great Neighborhood w/underground utilities, sidewalks, children's parks, picnic areas, & deeded sound access for swimming, kayaking, or paddle boarding! Fish off the pier or just sit & enjoy the beautiful water views with Navarre Beach as the backdrop! Call today to start living the dream!
